                            Aliens Lair
                            -----------
This game is freeware.
If you have a Public Domain disc collection, you are allowed to take this
game on your discs if you send me that disc.
If you want to distribute this game, you have to contact me.

Instructions
------------
After the titlescreen has appeared pressing the firebutton will start the
game.If you want to quit the game just press the left mousebutton at the
top left of the titlescreen. Aliens Lair has 5 Levels. At the beginning
each player has five lives. But you can get an extralife in the bonusround
after each levelend-monster if you shoot or collect all objects or if you
have a score over 10,000. If you press during the game the firebutton of the
second joystick the two-player-mode will be activated. The ships are
controlled by the Joystick. Pressing the firebutton will fire a shoot.
If there's no more life it's game over. If you press during the game both
mousebuttons the game is over and the titlescreen appears again.

Aliens Lair © 1994 by Frank Otto, Grelckstr. 27, 22529 Hamburg, Germany.
